(1, 1, '2024-11-04 00:30:43', '2024-11-04 00:30:43', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Hello world!', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world__trashed', '', '', '2024-11-06 00:53:10', '2024-11-05 17:53:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/ProjectCMS/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(2, 1, '2024-11-04 00:30:43', '2024-11-04 00:30:43', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>...or something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://localhost:8080/ProjectCMS/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Sample Page', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2024-11-04 00:30:43', '2024-11-04 00:30:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/ProjectCMS/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3, 1, '2024-11-04 00:30:43', '2024-11-04 00:30:43', '<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h1><strong>Chng ti l ai</strong></h1>\r\n<p>Vn bn  xut: Khi khch truy cp  li bnh lun trn trang web, chng ti thu thp d liu hin th trong biu mu bnh lun, cng nh a ch IP ca khch truy cp v chui tc nhn ngi dng ca trnh duyt  gip pht hin th rc.</p>\r\n<p>Mt chui n danh c to t a ch email ca bn (cn gi l bm) c th c cung cp cho dch v Gravatar  xem bn c ang s dng dch v  hay khng. Chnh sch bo mt ca dch v Gravatar c ti y: https://automattic.com/privacy/. Sau khi bnh lun ca bn c chp thun, nh h s ca bn s hin th cng khai trong bi cnh bnh lun ca bn.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Phng tin</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Vn bn  xut: Nu bn ti hnh nh ln trang web, bn nn trnh ti ln hnh nh c d liu v tr nhng (EXIF GPS). Khch truy cp trang web c th ti xung v trch xut bt k d liu v tr no t hnh nh trn trang web.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Cookie</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Vn bn  xut: Nu bn  li bnh lun trn trang web ca chng ti, bn c th chn lu tn, a ch email v trang web ca mnh trong cookie. Nhng iu ny nhm mc ch thun tin cho bn  bn khng phi in li thng tin chi tit ca mnh khi bn  li bnh lun khc. Nhng cookie ny s tn ti trong mt nm.</p>\r\n<p>Nu bn truy cp trang ng nhp ca chng ti, chng ti s thit lp mt cookie tm thi  xc nh xem trnh duyt ca bn c chp nhn cookie hay khng. Cookie ny khng cha d liu c nhn v s b xa khi bn ng trnh duyt.</p>\r\n<p>Khi bn ng nhp, chng ti cng s thit lp mt s cookie  lu thng tin ng nhp v la chn hin th mn hnh ca bn. Cookie ng nhp tn ti trong hai ngy v cookie ty chn mn hnh tn ti trong mt nm. Nu bn chn \"Ghi nh ti\", thng tin ng nhp ca bn s tn ti trong hai tun. Nu bn ng xut khi ti khon, cookie ng nhp s b xa.</p>\r\n<p>Nu bn chnh sa hoc xut bn mt bi vit, mt cookie b sung s c lu trong trnh duyt ca bn. Cookie ny khng bao gm d liu c nhn v ch cho bit ID bi ng ca bi vit bn va chnh sa. N ht hn sau 1 ngy.</p>\r\n<p>Ni dung c nhng t cc trang web khc</p>\r\n<p>Vn bn c  xut: Cc bi vit trn trang web ny c th bao gm ni dung c nhng (v d: video, hnh nh, bi vit, v.v.). Ni dung c nhng t cc trang web khc hot ng theo cng mt cch chnh xc nh khi khch truy cp  truy cp trang web khc.</p>\r\n<p>Cc trang web ny c th thu thp d liu v bn, s dng cookie, nhng thm thng tin theo di ca bn th ba v theo di tng tc ca bn vi ni dung c nhng , bao gm theo di tng tc ca bn vi ni dung c nhng nu bn c ti khon v  ng nhp vo trang web .</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti chia s d liu ca bn vi ai</p>\r\n<p>Vn bn  xut: Nu bn yu cu t li mt khu, a ch IP ca bn s c bao gm trong email t li mt khu.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti lu gi d liu ca bn trong bao lu</p>\r\n<p>Vn bn  xut: Nu bn  li bnh lun, bnh lun v siu d liu ca bnh lun  s c lu gi v thi hn. iu ny l  chng ti c th t ng nhn dng v chp thun bt k bnh lun tip theo no thay v gi chng trong hng i kim duyt.</p>\r\n<p>i vi ngi dng ng k trn trang web ca chng ti (nu c), chng ti cng lu tr thng tin c nhn m h cung cp trong h s ngi dng ca h. Tt c ngi dng c th xem, chnh sa hoc xa thng tin c nhn ca h bt k lc no (tr khi h khng th thay i tn ngi dng ca mnh). Qun tr vin trang web cng c th xem v chnh sa thng tin .</p>\r\n<p>Bn c nhng quyn g i vi d liu ca mnh</p>\r\n<p>Vn bn  xut: Nu bn c ti khon trn trang web ny hoc   li bnh lun, bn c th yu cu nhn tp d liu c nhn  xut m chng ti lu gi v bn, bao gm mi d liu bn  cung cp cho chng ti. Bn cng c th yu cu chng ti xa mi d liu c nhn m chng ti lu gi v bn. iu ny khng bao gm bt k d liu no m chng ti c ngha v phi gi cho mc ch hnh chnh, php l hoc bo mt.</p>\r\n<p>Ni d liu ca bn c gi n</p>\r\n<p>Vn bn  xut: Bnh lun ca khch truy cp c th c kim tra thng qua dch v pht hin th rc t ng.</p>', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'privacy-policy', '', '', '2024-11-07 10:11:33', '2024-11-07 03:11:33', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/ProjectCMS/?page_id=3', 0, 'page', '', 0),
