(302, 1, '2024-11-06 00:45:44', '2024-11-05 17:45:44', '<h2 id=\"article_sapo\" class=\"cate-24h-foot-arti-deta-sum ctTp tuht_show\"><strong>Apple  vo cuc iu tra sau khi mt ngi ph n b bng nng khi chic iPhone 14 Pro Max ca c pht n trong lc c ang ng.</strong></h2>\r\nTheo thng tin t chng trnh Hui Bang Mang ca i pht thanh v truyn hnh Sn Ty (Trung Quc), s c xy ra vo khong 6:30 sng (gi a phng), khi ngi ph n ang ng gn chic iPhone ang sc. Khi c tr mnh, tay c v tnh chm vo ngn la ang bc chy t chic iPhone dn n vt bng nghim trng v nh thc c trong khung cnh khi la.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div id=\"container-24h-banner-in-image\">\r\n<div><img class=\"news-image initial loaded\" src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/4-2024/images/2024-11-05/3-1730791360-151-width740height495.jpg\" alt=\"Chic iPhone 14 Pro Max b bc chy hon ton sau v vic.\" data-original=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/4-2024/images/2024-11-05/3-1730791360-151-width740height495.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" data-adbro-processed=\"true\" />\r\n<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\">\r\n<div id=\"ADS_139_15s\" class=\"txtCent  \">\r\n<div class=\"text_adver_right\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"div-gpt-ad-1498551316151-57\" data-google-query-id=\"COaG_6XfxYkDFdfsTAIdihgrxA\">\r\n<div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/124557882/24h/vn/desktop/hitech_fashion/in_image_article_0__container__\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/124557882/24h/vn/desktop/hitech_fashion/in_image_article_0\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/124557882/24h/vn/desktop/hitech_fashion/in_image_article_0\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-load-complete=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"2\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"img_chu_thich_0407\">Chic<a class=\"TextlinkBaiviet\" title=\"iPhone 14\" href=\"https://www.24h.com.vn/iphone-14-c407e6579.html\">iPhone 14</a>Pro Max b bc chy hon ton sau v vic.</p>\r\nVideo ghi li hin trng cho thy thit hi xy ra l kh nghim trng: ging ca c b chy xm, tng cn h b khi lm en v chic iPhone cng b h hi nng. Cc cuc iu tra ban u cho thy pin ca in thoi c th  b trc trc dn n s c ny.\r\n\r\n<strong>iPhone 14 Pro Max ht bo hnh, Apple vn iu tra</strong>\r\n\r\nBo co cho bit ngi ph n trn  mua chic iPhone 14 Pro Max vo nm 2022, c ngha sn phm ny khng cn trong thi gian bo hnh. Tuy nhin, c vn ang tm kim cu tr li v nguyn nhn v n v hy vng c bi thng cho nhng thng tch v thit hi m c phi chu.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"news-image loaded\" src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/4-2024/images/2024-11-05/4-1730791385-664-width740height881.jpg\" alt=\"Cc vt dng b h hng do v chy gy ra.\" data-original=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/4-2024/images/2024-11-05/4-1730791385-664-width740height881.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" />\r\n<p class=\"img_chu_thich_0407\">Cc vt dng b h hng do v chy gy ra.</p>\r\nSau khi nhn c thng tin v s c lin quan n pin iPhone 14 Pro Max, nhm dch v khch hng ca Apple  by t s lo ngi. H khng nh rng bt k tnh trng bo hnh ca thit b, Apple s thu hi in thoi  tin hnh phn tch nhm xc nh nguyn nhn gy ra s c.\r\n\r\nApple nhn thc r mc  nghim trng ca tnh hnh v cam kt iu tra mi nguy c tim n v an ton lin quan n sn phm ca mnh. Tuy nhin, hin ti vn cha r liu pin trong in thoi c phi l pin chnh hng ca Apple hay thit b  tng tri qua sa cha no c th nh hng n tnh ton vn ca n, v i din Apple cho bit.\r\n\r\nS vic ny mt ln na nhn mnh mi nguy him khi t thit b sc m khng c ngi trng coi. Cc chuyn gia nhiu ln khuyn co khng nn sc in thoi qua m hoc  gn cc vt liu d chy nh ging.', 'Apple iu tra gp s c iPhone 14 Pro Max bc chy khi sc', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'apple-dieu-tra-gap-su-co-iphone-14-pro-max-boc-chay-khi-sac', '', '', '2024-11-06 00:45:44', '2024-11-05 17:45:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/ProjectCMS/?p=302', 0, 'post', '', 0),
