(308, 1, '2024-11-06 00:48:02', '2024-11-05 17:48:02', '<h2 id=\"article_sapo\" class=\"cate-24h-foot-arti-deta-sum ctTp tuht_show\"><strong>Ch vi ngy sau khi ra mt dng in thoi cao cp Xiaomi 15, hng  cng b gi thay linh kin chnh thc.</strong></h2>\r\nCh vi ngy sau khi ra mt dng in thoi cao cp Xiaomi 15, hng  cng b gi chnh thc cho cc linh kin thay th trn trang web ca mnh. Dng sn phm Xiaomi 15 c gii thiu vo ngy 29/10 vi mc gi khi im l 4.499 nhn dn t (khong 15.98 triu ng). Cc mu in thoi ni bt vi mn hnh OLED LTPO cong siu nh, chip Snapdragon 8 Elite v pin silicon carbon, h tr c sc c dy ln khng dy.\r\n\r\nThng tin v chi ph sa cha cho cc linh kin nh camera, mn hnh, pin v bo mch ch  c cng b, gip ngi dng nm r chi ph nu cn thay th. C s khc bit r rt v gi gia phin bn tiu chun v phin bn Pro ca Xiaomi 15. c bit, h thng camera sau trn phin bn Pro c chi ph sa cha cao hn.\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"container-24h-banner-in-image\">\r\n<div><img class=\"news-image initial loaded\" src=\"https://icdn.24h.com.vn/upload/4-2024/images/2024-11-05/Chi-phi-sua-chua-cua-Xiaomi-15-series-Ban-Pro-cao-hon-han-ban-thuong-1-1730773819-393-width900height600.jpg\" alt=\"Dng in thoi cao cp Xiaomi 15.\" data-original=\"https://icdn.24h.com.vn/upload/4-2024/images/2024-11-05/Chi-phi-sua-chua-cua-Xiaomi-15-series-Ban-Pro-cao-hon-han-ban-thuong-1-1730773819-393-width900height600.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" data-adbro-processed=\"true\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"img_chu_thich_0407\">Dng in thoi cao cp Xiaomi 15.</p>\r\nC th, vic thay ng knh tele trn Xiaomi 15 Pro c gi 430 nhn dn t (khong 1.53 triu ng), trong khi mu tiu chun ch tn 150 nhn dn t (khong 530 ngn ng). Tng t, camera chnh thay th trn Xiaomi 15 Pro c gi 345 nhn dn t (khong 1.23 triu ng), so vi 335 nhn dn t (khong 1.15 triu ng) ca phin bn tiu chun.\r\n\r\nChi ph sa cha mn hnh cng cho thy s khc bit gia hai mu my. Vic thay th mn hnh tiu chun trn c hai in thoi s tiu tn ca ngi dng 670 nhn dn t (khong 2.38 triu ng) hoc 730 nhn dn t (khong 2.59 triu ng) cho phin bn Bright Silver Edition. c bit, mn hnh Diamond Limited Edition c gi cao hn, ln ti 920 nhn dn t (khong 3.27 triu ng).\r\n\r\nChi ph thay th pin trn c hai mu in thoi l ging nhau, vi mc gi 119 nhn dn t (khong 420 ngn ng). Tuy nhin, gi thay th np pin li khc nhau ty theo mu my v phin bn. C th, vic thay v cho Xiaomi 15 Pro c gi 220 nhn dn t (khong 780 ngn ng), trong khi phin bn Bright Silver c gi 290 nhn dn t (khong 1.03 triu ng). V Diamond Limited Edition c gi cao nht, ln ti 360 nhn dn t (khong 1.28 triu ng).\r\n\r\nChi ph sa cha t nht thuc v vic thay th bo mch ch. Bo mch ch 12GB + 256GB cho Xiaomi 15 c gi 2.640 nhn dn t (khong 9.38 triu ng), trong khi linh kin tng t cho mu Pro ln ti 2.820 nhn dn t (khong 10 triu ng). Khong cch gi ny tip tc tng i vi cc cu hnh lu tr cao hn, vi bo mch ch 16GB + 1TB cho mu Pro c gi ln ti 3.370 nhn dn t (khong 11.97 triu ng).', 'Chi ph sa cha ca Xiaomi 15 series: Bn Pro cao hn hn bn thng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chi-phi-sua-chua-cua-xiaomi-15-series-ban-pro-cao-hon-han-ban-thuong', '', '', '2024-11-06 02:01:04', '2024-11-05 19:01:04', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/ProjectCMS/?p=308', 0, 'post', '', 0),
