cessed=\"true\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"img_chu_thich_0407\">iPhone 16 Pro c vin mn hnh mng hn ng k.</p>\r\nNi tm li, iPhone 16 Pro ng  mua, c bit nu bn ang s dng nhng chiciPhone c hn, c bit l th h iPhone 13 Pro tr v trc. Hin ti, sn phm ang c gi bn t 28,99 triu ng cho phin bn 256GB.\r\n\r\n<strong>u im iPhone 16 Pro:</strong>\r\n\r\n- Ln hn nhng khng cng knh\r\n\r\n- Thi lng pin di hn ng k\r\n\r\n- Ci tin camera, nt iu khincamera v Photographic Styles u vit\r\n\r\n- Apple Intelligence to nn s khc bit\r\n\r\n<strong>Nhc im:</strong>\r\n\r\n- Apple Intelligence vn cha sn sng\r\n\r\n- p my vn cha c thit k ph hp cho ntCamera Control\r\n\r\n- Nt hnh ng cha c nhiu ng dng thc t', 'Sau 1 thng, iPhone 16 Pro c ng mua khng?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sau-1-thang-iphone-16-pro-co-dang-mua-khong', '', '', '2024-11-06 02:00:51', '2024-11-05 19:00:51', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/ProjectCMS/?p=311', 0, 'post', '', 0),
