(319, 1, '2024-11-06 00:51:02', '2024-11-05 17:51:02', '<h2 id=\"article_sapo\" class=\"cate-24h-foot-arti-deta-sum ctTp tuht_show\"><strong>Apple ang m rng tha thun dch v v tinh iPhone, cam kt chi 1,1 t USD  m rng nng lc.</strong></h2>\r\nNh cung cp dch v v tinh GlobalStar tit l vic m rng tha thun vi<a class=\"TextlinkBaiviet\" title=\"Apple\" href=\"https://www.24h.com.vn/apple-c55e3987.html\">Apple</a>. Theo , Apple s cam kt chi thm 1,1 t USDcho cc khon thanh ton trc  phc v c s h tng, tng nng lc ca cc dch v v tinh. Ngoi ra, \"Nh To\" s nm gi 20% quyn s hu GlobalStartrong mt tha thun vn ch s hu tr gi khong 400 triu USD.\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"container-24h-banner-in-image\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img class=\"news-image initial loaded\" src=\"https://icdn.24h.com.vn/upload/4-2024/images/2024-11-02/Apple-chi-ca-ty-USD-cho-tinh-nang-nay-tren-iPhone----nh-ch---p-m--n-h--nh-2024-11-02-101017-1730541823-517-width952height479.png\" alt=\"nh minh ha.\" data-original=\"https://icdn.24h.com.vn/upload/4-2024/images/2024-11-02/Apple-chi-ca-ty-USD-cho-tinh-nang-nay-tren-iPhone----nh-ch---p-m--n-h--nh-2024-11-02-101017-1730541823-517-width952height479.png\" data-was-processed=\"true\" data-adbro-processed=\"true\" /></div>\r\n<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\">\r\n<div id=\"ADS_139_15s\" class=\"txtCent  \">\r\n<div class=\"text_adver_right\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"div-gpt-ad-1498551316151-57\" data-google-query-id=\"CNO62MzgxYkDFep1DwIdKWwMdA\">\r\n<div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/124557882/24h/vn/desktop/hitech_fashion/in_image_article_0__container__\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/124557882/24h/vn/desktop/hitech_fashion/in_image_article_0\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/124557882/24h/vn/desktop/hitech_fashion/in_image_article_0\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-load-complete=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"2\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"img_chu_thich_0407\">nh minh ha.</p>\r\nTin tc ny  khin c phiu GlobalStar tng vt v ch racc k hoch lnca Apple i vi cc tnh nng v tinh trn<a class=\"TextlinkBaiviet\" title=\"iPhone\" href=\"https://www.24h.com.vn/iphone-c407e1576.html\">iPhone</a>. V d, vi iOS 18, ngi dng iPhone hin c th gi tin nhn vn bn cho bn b v gia nh qua v tinhkhi nm ngoi phm vi sng di ng hoc WiFi.\r\n\r\nApple tip tc cung cp cc ngun ti chnh ng k  cung cp cc tnh nng v tinh, ng thi cung cp tnh nng ny min ph cho ngi dng. Tuy nhin, cng ty  nhiu ln m ch v vic c  nh tnh ph i vi ngi dng iPhone ti mt thi im no .\r\n\r\nKt ni v tinh cho Emergency SOS ln u tin ra mt vi dngiPhone 14 nm 2022. Vo thi im , Apple cho bit, tnh nng kt niv tinh s min ph trong hai nm. iu  c ngha l khch hng s phi bt u tr tin vo khong cui nm 2024. Tuy nhin, Apple  gia hn thi gian min ph n nm 2025.\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image loaded\" src=\"https://icdn.24h.com.vn/upload/4-2024/images/2024-11-02/Apple-chi-ca-ty-USD-cho-tinh-nang-nay-tren-iPhone-hq720-1730541823-336-width686height386.jpg\" alt=\"nh minh ha.\" data-original=\"https://icdn.24h.com.vn/upload/4-2024/images/2024-11-02/Apple-chi-ca-ty-USD-cho-tinh-nang-nay-tren-iPhone-hq720-1730541823-336-width686height386.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"img_chu_thich_0407\">nh minh ha.</p>\r\n\"To Khuyt\" vn cha xc nhn mc phcho cc tnh nng v tinh. y l mt ch  nhy cm v phn ln cc dch v hin ti u da vo vic s dng v tinh trong cc trng hp khn cp, e da tnh mng, iu ny khin Apple cm thy kh bt tin khi tnh ph. Kh nng cao lcng ty s tip tc cung cp Emergency SOS min ph, chtnh ph cho cc tnh nng khc nh kh nng chia s v tr trong Find My hoc kh nng iOS 18 mi  gi tin nhn vn bn qua v tinh  gii tr.\r\n\r\nTheo cc chuyn gia,dch v v tinh c th c a vo gi Apple One hoc c cung cp thng qua cc tin ch b sung ca nh mng di ng.\r\n\r\nKt ni v tinh  h tr trn iPhone 14 v cc mu<a class=\"TextlinkBaiviet\" title=\"iPhone mi\" href=\"https://www.24h.com.vn/iphone-c407e1576.html\">iPhone mi</a>hn. Thng thng, kt ni v tinh ch c kch hot khi nm ngoi phm vi di ng hoc WiFi. Tuy nhin, ngi dng c th dng th tnh nng kt ni v tinh  ch  demo trn in thoi ngay by gi bng cch iu hng n Ci t (Settings) -&gt; Emergency SOS -&gt; Emergency SOS qua v tinh -&gt; Dng th bn demo (Try Demo).', 'Apple chi thm t USD cho tnh nng ny trn iPhone', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '317-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-11-06 00:51:02', '2024-11-05 17:51:02', '', 317, 'http://localhost:8080/ProjectCMS/?p=319', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
